<p><a name="The_first_Persian_state:_Achaemenid_Persia" id="The_first_Persian_state:_Achaemenid_Persia"></a></p>
<h2>The first Persian state: Achaemenid Persia</h2>
<p>c.<a href="/wiki/648_BC" title="648 BC">648 BC</a>-<a href="/wiki/330_BC" title="330 BC">330 BC</a></p>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div style="width:302px;"><a href="/wiki/Image:Persepolis_1.JPG" class="internal" title="Excavations at "><img src=
"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c4/300px-Persepolis_1.JPG" alt="Excavations at " width="300" height="225"
longdesc="/wiki/Image:Persepolis_1.JPG" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify" style="float:right"><a href="/wiki/Image:Persepolis_1.JPG" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src=
